                                    "type": "text",
                                    "content": "We have investigated the short- timescale X- ray spectra corresponding to the high and low intensity phases of the LFQPO (defined as peak and trough) in one Insight- HXMT observation of MAXI"
                                }
                            ]
                        }
                    ],
                    "index": 5
                },
                {
                    "bbox": [
